import React from 'react'
import { View, Text, StyleSheet } from 'react-native'
import { FlatList } from 'react-native-gesture-handler'
import Question from '../components/Question'

const ArrayScreen = () => {
    return (
        <View>
            <Text>Let's Learn About Array</Text>
            <FlatList>    
                <Question source={require('../../assets/1.jpg')}/>
                <Question source={require('../../assets/2.jpg')}/>
                <Question source={require('../../assets/3.jpg')}/>
                <Question source={require('../../assets/4.jpg')}/>
                <Question source={require('../../assets/5.jpg')}/>
                <Question source={require('../../assets/6.jpg')}/>
            </FlatList>
        </View> 
    )
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({

})

export default ArrayScreen
